---
title: Steak and Chipotle Sauce with Crispy Potato and Charred Sweetcorn Hash
description: We went around for years pronouncing chipotle as 'chip-ottle' before anyone told us it was actually supposed to be 'cheepoat- lay'. Whichever way you say it, we love these smoked chillies and the heat that a bit of chipotle  paste brings to today's steak recipe. We think you will too!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/steak-and-chipotle-sauce-c97dd8bc.jpg
